CardDeck
by Avery Scott II

A simple Console program for creating, sorting, and shuffling a deck of playing cards.

Uses the NUnit 3.7.0 C# UnitTesting Framework.

Tested using the Visual Studio 2017 Community Mac edition & the Visual Studio 2015 Community Windows edition.
For testing in the VS 2015 Windows addition, download and install the NUnit 3 Test Adapter from:

https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=NUnitDevelopers.NUnit3TestAdapter
